23
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,410
雖然我只是在中途登上了這列火車
Even if I have got in the middle..

24
00:03:27,490 --> 00:03:29,910
故事從Mettu patti（印度南部一小鎮）開始
..this story begins in Mettu patti

25
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:35,330
陸軍少校Partha Sarathy的妻子Kanthimathi
The army major Partha Sarathy's wife Kanthimathi..

26
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:37,250
已經懷胎十月
..is pregnant for 10th month

27
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:41,170
Mettupatti附近就是我們的村莊Semmanoor
Mettupatti's neighborhood is our village called Semmanoor

28
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:44,340
Muthu Ramalingam控制著這個村莊
Muthu Ramalingam dominates the village!

29
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:46,430
是我 Mari 我是你的人
I am Mari speaking! I am your man.

30
00:03:46,510 --> 00:03:49,430
他已經知道了 他會殺了我的
He has come to know it.. He would kill me

31
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:55,400
- 救救我 - 你在哪里打電話
-Save me. -Where are you talking from?

32
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,360
我在Mettupatti koil大街
..from Mettupatti, Murugan koil street.

33
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:01,610
老大 別殺我
Sir! Don't kill me

34
00:04:01,690 --> 00:04:04,360
如果是可以信賴的敵人 也許我會饒了他
I can forgive my enemy if he can be trusted.

35
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:08,200
但如果是個叛徒 就算是我的兄弟 我也不會放過他
I can't forgive a betrayer even if he is my brother.

36
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:09,450
老大
Sir..

37
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:16,540
Muthu Ramalingam來到Mettu patti是為了取人性命
Muthu Ramalingam came to the village to take a life!

38
00:04:16,580 --> 00:04:20,300
可是兩條性命因他而得救 這并非出于偶然
But it is not a coincidence that 2 souls were saved because of him

39
00:04:20,340 --> 00:04:22,210
而是神的安排
That was god's calculation

40
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:24,880
誰給嬰兒取名 嬰兒就會繼承誰的品行
The infant will inherit the behavior of the one who names the infant.

41
00:04:25,010 --> 00:04:28,010
我不希望他像我一樣殘忍兇暴
So I expect him not to be brutal & vicious like me.

42
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,180
他要做個心靜如水的人
He should be a serene and calm soul!

43
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:32,220
就像孕育了一切的大地
..like the earth which bears everything.

44
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:33,600
我就以此為他取名
I will name him that.

45
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:34,850
Bhoominathan（在泰米爾語中是大地的意思）
Bhoominathan.

46
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:44,240
Ammukutty（女孩名）和Bhoomi Nathan
Ammukutty & Bhoomi Nathan!

47
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:47,860
為什么你要把名字擦掉
Why do you erase it off?

48
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:51,030
因為有個女孩的名字和我的名字寫在一起
Because a girl's name is written along with mine.

49
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,450
也許是因為她喜歡你呢
She might have liked you. That's why.

50
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:58,250
那這是你寫的哦 你就是Ammukutty
So, is it your work? Are you the Ammukutty?

51
00:05:00,250 --> 00:05:01,800
你在哪個班
Which class are you studying?

52
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:04,300
從小他就是這個樣子
He is like this since the childhood.

53
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:07,380
喜歡他的女孩子都對他敬而遠之
The girls admire him keeping a distance.

54
00:05:07,470 --> 00:05:11,810
大家都說長大以后想當醫生 工程師或律師 你卻說什么
All want to become a doctor, engineer, or a lawyer. What did you say?

55
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:14,390
- 你說你想做Shemmanoor Muthu Ramalingam那樣的人 - 是的 老師
-Do you want to become like Shemmanoor Muthu Ramalingam? -Yes sir

56
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:17,890
他給嬰兒取這名字是希望他心懷寧靜
He named the child so that he should be serene looking!

57
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,480
可是Bhoominathan卻
..but Bhoominathan

58
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,200
Bhoomi歡迎儀式還行吧
Bhoomi! How's the reception?

59
00:05:35,330 --> 00:05:37,330
- 歡迎誰 - 當然是你嘍
-For whom? -lt's for you!

60
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:48,300
還不錯 有個家伙和我名字一樣
Not bad. There is a guy in my name!

61
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:49,970
不是別人 叫的就是你
It is not somebody. lt is only you

62
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:53,470
去打倒他 把他塞進去
Go and get him. Send him in

63
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,560
- 你 - 快上
-You! -Go I say

64
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:02,230
他怎么倒了
How did he fall?

65
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:09,150
- 我們賺了150萬盧比 - 我什么都沒做啊
-15 lakhs are ours! -l didn't do anything.

66
00:06:13,330 --> 00:06:15,370
他有超能力不
Is he get any supernatural power?

67
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:20,670
好像背扭傷了
It seems there is a sprain in the back

68
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:27,960
是我贏了
It is me

69
00:06:29,050 --> 00:06:30,130
還有個人
There is another man.

70
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,150
怎么了
What happened?

71
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,360
我以為只是玩玩 沒想到他真打啊
I thought it is a game only. But he is really hitting me!

72
00:06:52,490 --> 00:06:54,240
那你也真打 別浪費時間
You too go. Don't waste any time.

73
00:08:33,300 --> 00:08:36,970
瞧瞧 我拿一成半 剩下的都歸你
Look! 15 percent is mine as commission! The rest is yours.

74
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:39,510
拿去給你姐姐辦嫁妝吧
Use it for your sister's marriage!

75
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:42,060
以后別叫我做這種事了
Don't call me for such things any more!

76
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:51,730
嗎
Mom!

77
00:08:54,650 --> 00:08:55,450
老媽
Mother..

78
00:08:55,530 --> 00:08:57,360
你回來了啊
Have you come?

79
00:08:57,450 --> 00:08:58,370
你這些天都跑哪去了啊
Where were you all this time?

80
00:08:58,450 --> 00:08:59,740
我說過我去了
I told you before I went..

81
00:08:59,830 --> 00:09:01,910
我去參加朋友Shiva他姐姐的婚禮了
..that I am going to my friend Shiva's sister's marriage!

82
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:06,000
婚禮在Kumbakonam 你跑到曼谷去做什么
Marriage is in Kumbakonam! Why did you go to Bangkok before that?

83
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:09,540
你兒子一直是本地的小混混
Your son were being a rogue locally!

84
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:12,090
- 現在開始混到國外去了 - 我
Now he has started to go abroad! I am..

85
00:09:12,170 --> 00:09:13,550
- 舅舅 - 你干嘛老是要我操心啊
-Uncle! -Why are you bothering me?

86
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:15,760
- 他說的都是真的 - 是真的 老媽
-ls it true what he says? -Yes mom!

87
00:09:16,090 --> 00:09:17,470
干得好
Well done

88
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:19,760
你去賽拳就是為了錢
He was in the competition to earn money.

89
00:09:19,930 --> 00:09:23,010
總有一天他會為了錢去殺人
He would become a killer just for money.

90
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:24,680
這就是我的命
It is my fate.

91
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:28,480
我早就知道 
I thought when he named the child..

92
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:30,560
讓Muthu Ramalingam給孩子取名 孩子一定會繼承他的惡性
I was sure he would inherit the qualities of Muthu Ramalingam.

93
00:09:30,690 --> 00:09:33,440
他已經不做違法勾當了
He has stopped the criminal activities.

94
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:35,740
他現在是村莊的保護傘
..and has become the Godman of his village.

95
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:37,530
他必須要讓這個孩子轉性
He has to make this guy good.

96
00:09:37,610 --> 00:09:39,240
我一直在這么想
That's what I was thinking about.

97
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:42,530
以后再也不能讓他做違法的事了
No criminal activities from him, are allowed in future here.

98
00:09:43,830 --> 00:09:46,000
帶著這條笨狗 我到現在都沒找到家
I couldn't find this address yet..

99
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,080
他必須要讓這個孩子轉性 
..when I am searching with this dog.

100
00:09:48,170 --> 00:09:52,540
再這樣下去 我都要累成狗樣了
If I go like this, I'll be exhausted like this dog.

101
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:54,460
我覺得這里就是了
I think that it is the one.

102
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:58,550
- 這里就是Bhoomi - 叫他Bhoomi老大
-This is Bhoomi.. -Call him Bhoomi sir.

103
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:00,430
誰要是再敢直呼他的英名
If anyone calls him only his name hereafter..

104
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:01,550
就要承擔一切惡果
..he will face the consequences.

105
00:10:05,270 --> 00:10:07,100
這不是間房子 這是間寺廟
This is not a house but a temple.

106
00:10:07,350 --> 00:10:09,390
他不是Bhoomi 他是我的大神
He is not Bhoomi but my Samy(God).

107
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:13,110
Bhoomi出來吧
Bhoomi! Come out.

108
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:21,700
那是誰 老爸 是你朋友嗎
Who is it dad? Is he your friend?

109
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:23,910
我是你的助手
I am your Assistant!

110
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:28,000
讓我留下來做你的助手吧 你的生命會因此而閃耀
Keep me as your assistant! Your life will be bright.

111
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,710
- 你是誰 - 噢 天哪
-Who are you? -Oh god!

112
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,710
我跪著 你卻站在邊上看
You are watching while I am bowing down.

113
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:34,750
你和我一起跪 這樣才會答應我們留下來
You too have to bow down. Only then we both can be with him!

114
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,380
- 老大 狗狗的埔士不錯吧 - 站起來
-Boss! How is my dog's pose? -Get up!

115
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:39,630
我不起來 你得接受我
I won't. You have to commit me

116
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,640
- 接受我 - 那是誰啊
-Commit -Who is that?

117
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:43,760
為什么一大清早就堵在我們家門口
He has come and blocked the way in the early morning!

118
00:10:43,850 --> 00:10:45,640
- 我有么 - 給我起來
-Am l like that? -Hey, get up man

119
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,640
我有問過你要助手嗎
Did I ask you for an assistant?

120
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:49,270
難道人們為Muruga神削發也要征得同意
（Muruga：印度教戰神 也被稱為泰米爾人之神）
Does one tonsure his head for Lord Murugan?

121
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:50,350
難道出席葬禮穿喪服也要遺體同意
Does one wear dress seeing the body?

122
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:52,480
同樣我不需要你的同意就能做你的保鏢
Like wise I have joined as a bodyguard for you without your permission

123
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:54,560
告訴我 你要我去砍誰
Tell me now. You show me him now

124
00:10:54,650 --> 00:10:56,480
我立馬就去把他剁了
I will chop him off then and there.

125
00:10:56,570 --> 00:10:58,030
他問你呢 告訴他
He is asking you. Tell him.

126
00:10:58,110 --> 00:10:59,860
- 鼓起勇氣來 - 讓他砍我吧
-Take courage! -Let him chop me away.

127
00:10:59,950 --> 00:11:00,860
砍他
Is it him?

128
00:11:00,950 --> 00:11:04,570
你還嫌這里不夠亂啊 走開
He is adding more problems! Go

129
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:06,790
我能把包和狗留下嗎
Can l leave the bag and dog here?

130
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:08,500
它看著就像條流浪狗
He looks like a street dog!

131
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:12,670
嗨 你可以侮辱我 但你不能侮辱我兄弟
Look! You can abuse me, but not my brother

132
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,580
它不是你說的流浪狗
He is not a street dog as you say.

133
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:18,210
你瞧著 我來證明它是頭雄獅
You can watch it. I will prove that he is a lion!

134
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,800
這是個球兄弟
This is a ball. Brother.

135
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:26,810
好了 真不錯
That's it. Fine!

136
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:28,310
瞧見了嗎 老大
Have you seen it boss?

137
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:30,600
它把球撿回來了
He has brought back the ball!

138
00:11:30,690 --> 00:11:32,810
我整整整訓練了他3年
I gave him training for 3 years for this act.

139
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:35,230
3年才教會它撿球 
3 years for retrieving the ball?

140
00:11:35,310 --> 00:11:37,570
你自己只要一分鐘就能把球撿回來
You could bring it in 2 minute as well!

141
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:43,950
- 老大 瞧瞧這是什么 - 一把劍 
-Boss! What is this? -A sword!

142
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,660
我當年在Koduva Kummattha手下做事
When l was working with Koduva Kummattha..

143
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:48,450
因為事情做得很棒 他賞給我這把劍
..he gave me this gift for my good performance!

144
00:11:48,490 --> 00:11:51,040
這是Pitchuva Pakiri賞給我的
It is the gift Pitchuva Pakiri gave me!

145
00:11:51,290 --> 00:11:54,870
這是炸彈 Baskar給我的禮物 他怕了我了
This is the gift which Bomb Baskar gave me after he got afraid of me!

146
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:57,380
- 禮物 - 炸彈
-Gift? -Bomb!

147
00:11:57,670 --> 00:12:00,300
你拉這里 然后丟出去
If you pull this ring and throw it..

148
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,880
能炸爛一堆人
..a group will reduce to ruins!

149
00:12:01,970 --> 00:12:03,880
拉這里不
Is it the one?

150
00:12:03,970 --> 00:12:06,470
靠 它會爆炸的
Damn it. It will get blasted.

151
00:12:06,510 --> 00:12:08,510
- 那就把它扔了唄 - 沒錯
-Throw it if it would blast! -Yes..

152
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,970
噢 天哪
Oh god!

153
00:12:13,980 --> 00:12:16,600
- 喔 我的兄弟叼起來了 - 啊 神哪
-Whoa! My brother took it. -Oh god!

154
00:12:16,690 --> 00:12:19,230
他要叼回來還給我
He is coming to return to me!

155
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,900
老大 救救我
Boss! Please save me.

156
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:22,900
它改變路線了
He has changed the route.

157
00:12:22,990 --> 00:12:26,990
這不是包子 這是炸彈 快扔掉
It is not a bun but a bomb! Throw it down.

158
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:44,800
鬼啊 妖怪啊
Ghost.. Devil..

159
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,340
狗啊
Dog..

160
00:12:48,890 --> 00:12:52,100
來了 大兄弟 你在哪里
Come brother! Where are you?

161
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:53,180
我在這兒
I am here.

162
00:12:53,350 --> 00:12:54,270
大兄弟來了
Brother has come

163
00:12:54,350 --> 00:12:55,940
大兄弟 你手上拿的是什么
What in law.. with a cover in your hand?

164
00:12:56,190 --> 00:12:57,270
是調你去Shemmanoor的調令
Is it the transfer to Shemmanoor?

165
00:12:57,350 --> 00:12:59,190
不是 是保護令
No. Protection duty!

166
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:01,730
Semmanoor Muthu Ramalingam有生命危險
Semmanoor Muthu Ramalingam's life is in danger!

167
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:05,240
他們要調我去那里保護他
So for his protection they have transferred me to there.

168
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:08,910
Muthanna有生命危險 出什么事了
Is Muthanna's life in danger? What happened?

169
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:12,580
妹夫 只要你打個電話給他
In-law! If you call Muthu Ramalingam and tell him..

170
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:15,120
他肯定會拒絕警方保護
..he would refuse to take police protection.

171
00:13:15,210 --> 00:13:16,620
那我們的擔子就算放下了
Our burden will be eased off.

172
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:19,500
舅舅 你還算是個警察嗎
Uncle! Are you a true policeman?

173
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:22,630
上頭給你保護任務 你卻想逃避
When you are given the escort duty you tend to escape from that.

174
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:24,550
