176
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:30,430
這是要求保護生命的政府公務
This is the government order to protect a life.

177
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:33,350
就算讓我去 那也是對命令的尊重
Even if I go, it will be a respect for the order.

178
00:13:33,430 --> 00:13:35,890
你管這個干什么 不要多管閑事
Why do you need all these? You mind your business.

179
00:13:36,350 --> 00:13:39,560
