他要是起疑 拆開來看了怎么辦
What if he reads it after getting the doubt?

183
00:13:49,950 --> 00:13:52,490
他不會對自己相信的人起疑的
He won't doubt anyone whom he believes!

184
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:54,080
