SEMMANOOR Municipality. Welcomes you!

187
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:04,170
快上來 往里擠
Come up! Climb up!

188
00:14:11,890 --> 00:14:13,720
拿好票 零頭待會找
Take it. Give the change later

189
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:20,020
你去哪
Where are you going?

190
00:14:20,230 --> 00:14:23,730
我去Semmanoor Muthuramalingm家執行保護任務
I'm going to Semmanoor Muthuramalingm's house on protection duty.

191
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,730
過來坐這吧 我讓位子給你
You come and sit here. I'll get up.

192
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:28,110
不 不 還是你坐吧
No. You can sit there.

193
00:14:29,490 --> 00:14:30,490
我馬上下車了 你坐吧
I'll get down now

194
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:33,660
把小孩給我 我讓他坐我腿上
Give the baby to me. I'll put it on my lap!

195
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:34,910
沒事的 你坐下
It's okay, you sit down!

196
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,660
沒事的 坐我腿上好了
It's ok! I'll put it on my lap

197
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:42,210
她和我打招呼 然后又叫我坐在她腿上
She called me.. and then asking me to sit on her lap.

198
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:44,500
還等什么快來
Why do you hesitate? Come

199
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:49,720
不行啊 車上人太多了
No. The bus is crowded.

200
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:50,880
我們私底下再坐吧
We shall have it in privacy!

201
00:14:51,430 --> 00:14:55,810
- 和你說了 過來吧 - 這可不行
-Tell you to come to me. -This won't work out.

202
00:14:55,890 --> 00:14:59,980
- 我得表現得有種些 - 快來 快過來 - 來了 來了 別急
-l have to show my worth. -Come. Come to me. -Coming. Don't be hurry

203
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:02,650
這樣看上去不錯吧 你叫什么叫啊
Does it look good? Why do you yell up?

204
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:06,570
- 狗日的 快起來 - 出什么事了
-Damn it! Get up -What happened?

205
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:09,990
聽我解釋 要打連她一塊兒打
Listen to me.. Beat her too

206
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:11,820
聽我說 我的老大在那邊看著呢
Look.. My boss is looking

207
00:15:11,910 --> 00:15:13,570
他來這里干什么 欠揍啊
Why has he come here and getting beaten up?

208
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,910
你知道你打的是誰嗎
Do you know who you are beating?

209
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,450
你打的是警察 一位要去
You have beaten the police officer who is..

210
00:15:19,540 --> 00:15:22,290
Semmanoor Muthu Ramalingam家保護他的警察
..going to Semmanoor Muthu Ramalingam's house for protection!

211
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:26,000
我不是一個人 從在那里的那位警官
I'm not alone. The inspector who is sitting there..

212
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:27,210
是和我一起的
..is coming with me.

213
00:15:28,010 --> 00:15:30,590
- 為什么他需要保護 - 因為他有生命危險
-Why does he need protection? -His life is in danger!

214
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:31,840
他是去當保鏢的
He is going as his bodyguard.

215
00:15:31,930 --> 00:15:33,130
我是負責護送他的
I am going with him as an escort.

216
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,840
你打我就等于打他
You are beating him without knowing it.

217
00:15:34,930 --> 00:15:36,760
你去請求他原諒你
You ask him to pardon you.

218
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:39,020
否則我把你們全射死在車里
Or else, I'll shoot down all in the bus!

219
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:44,020
警官 我剛才不知道您是誰才問您收車票錢的
Sir! I issued the ticket without knowing who you are.

220
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:45,310
請收回你的錢
Please get back your money.

221
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:47,070
走開 走開
Go man! Move away.

222
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:53,740
- 轉過身去 - 沒問題
-Turn back. -l will.

223
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,070
媽啊
Mom!

224
00:15:58,370 --> 00:16:01,790
要是你再跟著我 靠
If you come behind me again.. Oh god!

225
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,420
- Valli妹妹 Meera在哪里呢 - 她在樓上
-Valli sister. Where is Meera? -She is upstairs.

226
00:16:16,970 --> 00:16:17,760
你在哪里
Where are you?

227
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:23,390
你家來了個保鏢
A bodyguard has come to your house.

228
00:16:23,770 --> 00:16:25,060
保鏢 為什么
Bodyguard? Why?

229
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:27,150
你爸爸有生命危險
Your dad's life is in danger.

230
00:16:27,230 --> 00:16:29,400
保鏢是來保護他的
The bodyguard has come for his protection!

231
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:31,070
是誰胡說八道
Who has told this foolishness?

232
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:33,440
胡說八道 是我爸告訴我的
Foolishness? My dad has told me that.

233
00:16:33,530 --> 00:16:34,860
你爸走著路都能睡著
He sleeps when he walks!

234
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:36,410
也許是他說夢話胡扯來著
He would have blabbered this in his dream!

235
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:41,410
這里就是Semmanoor府邸 進來吧
This is the Semmanoor place. Please come.

236
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:45,710
Muthu Ramalingam就生于此長于此
This is where Muthu Ramalingam was born and brought up.

237
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:47,920
他現在不在家 他在迪拜
He is not here now. He is in Dubai.

238
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:51,380
你坐今晚的航班回印度 然后就回家
He will come in the evening flight. He will be here after that.

239
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:58,010
- 先生 - 請進
-Sir! -Please come.

240
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:04,930
- 請進 這是女主人Devika太太 - 您好
-Please come. She is his wife! Devika madam. -Greetings!

241
00:17:05,020 --> 00:17:08,860
他是來保護主人的 他是Mohan Raj警官
He has come for the protection of sir! He is Inspector Mohan Raj.

242
00:17:09,020 --> 00:17:10,480
先生 我叫Bhoomi Nathan
Bhoomi Nathan, sir!

243
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:13,150
我叫Chakrapani 我是主人唯一的管家
Chakrapani, I'm the only manager to sir!

244
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:16,400
我很警覺 就算是影子都潛不進來
I am very alert that even a shadow wouldn't enter here.

245
00:17:16,490 --> 00:17:19,490
這里沒有他的仇人
When there are no enemies for him in this place..

246
00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:22,160
我不知道為什么他需要人來保護
..I wonder why he needs a protection!

247
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:24,700
- Chakra兄弟 - 我正要問他
-Chakra brother! -l was asking that to him.

248
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,500
他在這里有仇家嗎
Does he have any enemies here?

249
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,540
危險不僅僅來自于仇家
Danger can come not only from the enemies!

250
00:17:28,630 --> 00:17:31,040
有時危險就來自于周圍的人
But it can be from the people around.

251
00:17:35,970 --> 00:17:37,970
這是屋子的大廳
This is the main hall of this house!

252
00:17:38,890 --> 00:17:40,720
- 他就是那個保鏢 - 沒錯
-ls he the bodyguard? -Yes!

253
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:44,060
- 你說什么 - 她就是主人的女兒Meera
-What? -She is sir's daughter Meera!

254
00:17:49,190 --> 00:17:50,690
Meera 他把我當成你了
Meera! He took me for you!

255
00:17:50,860 --> 00:17:51,690
就那樣好
Let it be like that.

256
00:17:51,770 --> 00:17:55,030
- 先生 - 來來 我們到處看看
-Sir! -Come. Let's go around the house.

257
00:17:55,690 --> 00:17:56,780
他往這邊來了
He is coming

258
00:17:58,320 --> 00:18:01,950
- 這里是院子 - 看看 他像個保鏢嗎
-This is the court yard. -Look! ls he like the bodyguard?

259
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:04,410
他就像個男仆一樣要看遍我們的家
He wants to go around our home like the groom

260
00:18:09,630 --> 00:18:13,170
只要我在這里 就沒什么進得了這個屋子
Nothing will enter into this house still I am here

261
00:18:14,170 --> 00:18:15,420
主人的房間在樓上 
Sir's room is in the upstairs

262
00:18:17,260 --> 00:18:18,170
哦 天哪
Oh god!

263
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:27,430
是誰
Who is it?

264
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:29,440
誰扎破了氣球 是誰
Who has cracked he balloon? Who?

265
00:18:32,190 --> 00:18:33,900
- 你盯著我看什么 - 不是我
-Why do you stare at me? -lt is not me.

266
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:35,570
是你自己睡著了
It's you after your sleep.

267
00:18:47,290 --> 00:18:48,500
一支箭
An arrow!

268
00:18:48,580 --> 00:18:49,830
從哪里來的
Where has it come from now?

269
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:52,290
從我頭上拿下來的嗎
Is it from my head?

270
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,630
作哦一名保鏢 你應該帶著勇氣而來
As a bodyguard, you should've come with energy (Thembu).

271
00:18:54,710 --> 00:18:56,050
而不是帶著箭（泰米爾語中勇氣是Thembu 箭是Ambu 讀音近似）
..not with an arrow (ambu)

272
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:00,130
他看上去身手不錯哦
He looks very smart!

273
00:19:02,430 --> 00:19:04,510
他過來了 快躲起來 快
He is coming! Escape. Go.

274
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:07,270
噢 快
Oops! Go..

275
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:10,060
- 那我去機場接主人了 - 行 你去吧
-l'll meet sir in the airport -Ok. You may go.

276
00:19:21,990 --> 00:19:25,200
- 你是誰 - 她嗎 - 她在Meera的廠里做工
-Who are you? -She..! -She works in Meera's factory!

277
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:26,830
那她為什么在這里而不待在廠里
Why is she here instead of the factory?

278
00:19:26,910 --> 00:19:29,000
我們是來看你的
We have come to see you.

279
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:34,210
- 看我 - 我們還從沒親眼參觀過保鏢呢
-Why? -We haven't seen a bodyguard as a whole.

280
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:36,920
你在開玩笑吧 我看著像個小丑嗎
Are you teasing? Do I look like a buffoon?

281
00:19:38,010 --> 00:19:40,460
為了安全起見 未經允許 誰都不許踏進這個院了
None is allowed to come unnecessarily to this compound.

282
00:19:41,380 --> 00:19:43,010
你憑什么這么說 我們會經常來的
We will come at times! Who are you to tell that?

283
00:19:43,090 --> 00:19:45,600
這個油腔滑調的是誰 你們的工會主席嗎
Who is this smarty? Is it the union leader?

284
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:48,470
在廠里隨你怎么玩 在這里不行
You can have this nonsense in your factory. Not here.

285
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:52,310
啊 我的頭要炸了
Whoa! My head has exploded!

286
00:19:52,390 --> 00:19:56,270
他們打中我了 把我打死了
They have shot me! Shot me! Shot me to death.

287
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,730
MADURAI機場
MADURAI AIRPORT

288
00:20:03,450 --> 00:20:05,280
哈 那是我的人
Whao! lt's my man.

289
00:20:05,910 --> 00:20:07,160
他去哪里了
Where has he gone?

290
00:20:07,660 --> 00:20:09,080
剛才還在這里的
He was here.

291
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:16,500
- 你來這里做什么 - 什么 老大 你干了什么
-What is going on? -What boss? What have you done?

292
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:18,670
Muthu Ramalingam和他兒子要坐飛機來了
Muthu Ramalingam and his son are coming in the flight.

293
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:20,000
我們必須要保證安全 對嗎
We have to provide security for them, right?

294
00:20:20,090 --> 00:20:22,010
那沒錯 可現在又沒下雨
It is ok. lt is not raining now.

295
00:20:22,090 --> 00:20:24,840
- 你穿著雨衣做什么 - 雨衣
-Why do you wear a rain coat? -Rain coat?

296
00:20:25,390 --> 00:20:27,090
這是獨一無二的裝備
This is an unique outfit.

297
00:20:27,180 --> 00:20:28,760
有大用途的外套
A dress with good sense!

298
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:30,470
磁力外套
Magnetic dress!

299
00:20:31,770 --> 00:20:34,190
- 磁力外套 - 沒錯 老大
-Magnetic dress? -Yes boss

300
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:35,850
這就是磁力外套
The magnetic dress

301
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:41,190
只要機場里有任何鐵質的武器 它都能找出來
This dress will find out the iron weapons if any in this airport!

302
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:42,780
暴露在我們的面前
It can reveal them to us!

303
00:20:47,030 --> 00:20:50,200
啊 我的天哪
Oh my God!

304
00:20:52,330 --> 00:20:54,330
一支槍貼在我身上
A rifle is on my body

305
00:20:54,710 --> 00:20:57,580
快拉開
Pull it out.

306
00:20:57,670 --> 00:20:59,750
快掰下來
Snatch it away.

307
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,670
你算什么警察 快掰開來
What a police you are! Snatch it away

308
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:05,170
靠 我讓你掰下來 你開什么槍啊
Damn it. You are shooting instead of snatch it.

309
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:07,260
天哪 別開槍
Oh god! Don't shoot

310
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:10,180
把槍口朝天上
Place it in upward direction

311
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:12,680
完了
Oops!

312
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:17,350
謝天謝地
Thank god!

313
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,200
老大 你吩咐
Tell me boss.

314
00:21:33,290 --> 00:21:36,620
Muthu Ramalingam出來了 干掉他
Muthu Ramalingam is coming out. Finish him.

315
00:21:36,870 --> 00:21:37,870
是 老大
OK sir.

316
