你看不見 他在后面
Can't you see? He is there.

321
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:50,530
我不是問Karthi
I didn't ask for Karthi!

322
00:22:50,570 --> 00:22:53,160
- 我是問那個保鏢 - 誰 - 那個保鏢
-l was asking for the bodyguard. -Who? -lt is him

323
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:55,740
他去機場接機了 你沒看到他嗎
He has come to receive you in the airport. Didn't you see him?

324
00:22:55,910 --> 00:22:58,330
