Yes! That's why he has been allotted space in the out house.

332
00:23:13,390 --> 00:23:15,050
你們不長腦子的嗎
Don't you have sense?

333
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,060
陌生人說什么就是什么
You believe strangers what they say!

334
00:23:17,140 --> 00:23:18,600
他們要什么就給什么嗎
..and provide what they ask for, right?

335
00:23:20,810 --> 00:23:22,730
