Sir! I am here. Tell me.

336
00:23:22,980 --> 00:23:24,730
我不需要什么保鏢
I don't need a bodyguard.

337
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:28,320
- 不管他是誰 打發他走 聽到了嗎 - 好的 主人
-Send them back whoever it is. OK? -Right sir.

338
00:23:33,990 --> 00:23:36,490
爸爸就是那樣的 別打發他走
Dad is like that. Don't send them back.

339
00:23:36,740 --> 00:23:39,410
我們需要那樣的人保護我們的安全
We need a guy like that for our safety.

340
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:42,420
