Chakra! Don't sleep. Make arrangements for them to go.

561
00:40:23,500 --> 00:40:28,040
是 主人 明天你就和她們一起走吧
Ok, Sir. Tomorrow you are going with them.

562
00:40:28,130 --> 00:40:31,300
