He shouldn't behave like a student in the college.

572
00:41:02,460 --> 00:41:05,920
- 他要看上去像個保鏢 - 不用擔心 太太
-He should be a bodyguard! -Don't worry madam.

573
00:41:06,130 --> 00:41:09,540
無論Meera去哪里 我都形影不離
I'll be a shadow for Meera wherever she go.

574
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:11,380
這才是稱職的保鏢
..like a perfect bodyguard.

575
00:41:20,430 --> 00:41:24,100
第一天報到的新生們
Students who have come for the 1st day of the college..

576
00:41:24,190 --> 00:41:28,350
作為這所學校最勇敢的人 號稱校之雄獅的本人
This university's courageous guy lion of the college.

577
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:30,900
代表所有人歡迎新生代表
I welcome the leader on behalf of all!

578
