你沒腦子嗎
Don't you have sense?

583
00:41:54,050 --> 00:41:56,220
一朵玫瑰花才比較適合我
A rose flower is apt for me.

584
00:41:56,300 --> 00:41:59,390
快點拿給我 有人會拌跤摔死的 拿給我
Take it fast. Someone will against it and die. Take it.

585
00:42:03,220 --> 00:42:04,390
像小山一樣重
It seems like a hill.

586
00:42:12,530 --> 00:42:16,990
- 那是誰 - 等等 我讓你們下車你們再下
-Who is that? -Wait! Get down only after I tell you.

587
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:37,380
哦 天哪
Oh God!

588
