她穿得可真傻
His outfit looks silly.

589
00:42:44,390 --> 00:42:47,140
大家都在望著我們 
All are looking at us.

590
00:42:47,390 --> 00:42:50,810
盡管讓他們看 要讓所有人都知道我是你們的保鏢
Let them watch us. Let them know that l'm your bodyguard.

591
00:42:51,190 --> 00:42:52,270
所以我才穿套制服來的
This uniform is for that only.

592
00:42:55,530 --> 00:42:57,530
你是穿保鏢的衣服跟她們去學校的嗎
Have you gone with them in the bodyguard's attire?

593
00:42:58,650 --> 00:43:00,030
還記得我交待你的話嗎
Do you remember what l told you?

594
00:43:00,360 --> 00:43:03,580
你們現在在哪里 到學校了嗎
Where are you now? Have you reached the college?

595
00:43:03,660 --> 00:43:07,290
是 太太 Meera和Madhu正在去教室的路上
Yes madam! Meera and Madhu are going to their classes!

596
