在你以前的學校你就是個不良分子
You were a rowdy in the college you studied.

601
00:43:30,100 --> 00:43:31,020
很多人都和我這樣說了
Many people told me that.

602
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:33,150
但我還是接受了你入學
But you were given admission in this college.

603
00:43:33,230 --> 00:43:35,400
你知道為什么嗎 因為我看過你的成績單
Do you know why? After seeing your mark sheet only.

604
00:43:36,940 --> 00:43:38,400
你本可以拿第2名的
You could be No.2 in the university..

605
00:43:38,490 --> 00:43:41,490
只要你別混日子 而是好好讀書的話
..if you hadn't been a rowdy in the college and if you studied well.

606
00:43:44,030 --> 00:43:47,120
不過現在在這里 你還是有機會榜上有名的
You have chances to become a rank holder even now.

607
00:43:47,160 --> 00:43:49,660
