He is doing unnecessary talk

608
00:43:50,830 --> 00:43:53,460
只是因為這個原因 我才原諒你這一次
You have been pardoned off for this only reason..

609
00:43:53,540 --> 00:43:54,830
而不是開除你 明白嗎
..without dismissing you! Understand?

610
00:43:55,710 --> 00:43:58,710
要是你再以保鏢的名義進入女廁所
If you go to the ladies toilet again in the pretext of your duty...

611
00:43:58,840 --> 00:44:00,010
沒有你的命令我不會再進去了
I won't go unless you tell me.

612
00:44:00,090 --> 00:44:01,720
- 好 去吧 - 去女廁所嗎
-Ok go. -To the ladies toilet?

613
00:44:01,930 --> 00:44:03,840
