是 上課時要集中注意力
That is.. You should concentrate in the class!

629
00:46:13,100 --> 00:46:14,770
要是你老是東張西望的 你怎么可能學明白
If you look here and there, you won't be able to understand.

630
00:46:15,060 --> 00:46:17,690
你是來學校讀書的還是來走時裝秀的
Are you coming to the college to study or for the fashion parade?

631
