上往鎮子方向的末班車
..you take 2 tickets up to its last town and get into that

1679
02:04:09,400 --> 02:04:10,270
我會等在里面的
I will be in that.

1680
02:04:14,780 --> 02:04:17,110
你說過你也想見見你父母 是嗎
You told that you want to see your parents. lsn't it?

1681
02:04:17,400 --> 02:04:18,950
那就讓他們等在隨便哪一站
Ask them to come at any station.

1682
02:04:19,110 --> 02:04:20,160
我們見過他們再走
We will see them and go.

1683
02:04:20,320 --> 02:04:22,280
好 我會打電話通知他們
Ok, I'll call and inform them.

1684
02:04:23,330 --> 02:04:25,200
我會上你說的那列火車
I'll get into the train what you said to me.

1685
02:04:25,290 --> 02:04:30,420
如果你不在的話 那這將是我這輩子最后一趟旅程了
If you are not there that will be my last journey of life.

1686
02:04:33,790 --> 02:04:36,460
親愛的 那個保鏢騙了我們所有人
Dear, that bodyguard has cheated us.

1687
02:04:37,090 --> 02:04:38,550
他背叛我們了
He did betrayal for us.

1688
02:04:39,340 --> 02:04:42,340
他要和Meera私奔
He is to elope with our Meera.

1689
02:04:45,680 --> 02:04:48,480
他對我們家懷有敬意
He has much respect on our family.

1690
02:04:49,230 --> 02:04:51,810
而且為人誠實
He is a honest person.

1691
02:04:52,610 --> 02:04:55,900
他也知道我不會饒恕叛徒的
He knows that l won't forgive the one who does the betrayal.

1692
02:04:55,980 --> 02:04:57,320
哎呀 不是那樣的
Oh God! It is not like that.

1693
02:04:57,570 --> 02:04:58,860
是我們女兒的問題 
This is our daughter's matter.

1694
02:04:59,450 --> 02:05:00,990
Poonkodi剛剛告訴我
Poonkodi has just informed me.

1695
02:05:01,360 --> 02:05:03,870
她看見他們兩人通過手機交談了
She saw them in person when they spoke through the phone.

1696
02:05:16,340 --> 02:05:18,420
- 出大事了 - 什么事
-Big problem has happened. -What?

1697
02:05:18,880 --> 02:05:20,220
你出門后不久
After you have started from there..

1698
02:05:20,300 --> 02:05:22,590
有一伙人沖進來綁架了Meera
..a group of guys have come and kidnapped Meera.

1699
02:05:22,680 --> 02:05:24,180
綁架了Meera 你說什么
Kidnapped Meera? What are you saying?

1700
02:05:24,640 --> 02:05:25,970
是Devaraj派來的
They are Devaraj's men.

1701
02:05:26,060 --> 02:05:27,180
車已經上了高速
Vehicle is going in high way.

1702
02:05:27,310 --> 02:05:28,640
這是車號
This is that vehicle's number.

1703
02:05:35,190 --> 02:05:36,270
老板有何吩咐
Sir, tell me.

1704
02:05:36,360 --> 02:05:37,610
你們到哪里了
Where are you now?

1705
02:05:37,900 --> 02:05:39,480
我們已經過收費站了
We have crossed the toll gate.

1706
02:05:39,570 --> 02:05:42,490
- 不要停 開快些 - 是 老板
-Don't stop on the way and come fast. -Ok sir.

1707
02:06:00,130 --> 02:06:04,010
- 說 - 老板 Bhoomi跟上來了
-Tell me. -Sir, Bhoomi is following us.

1708
02:06:05,890 --> 02:06:07,430
不能讓他靠近我的女兒
He shouldn't come near my daughter.

1709
02:06:07,890 --> 02:06:09,260
隨便用什么手段都行
Do anything to him.

1710
02:06:09,930 --> 02:06:11,100
開快點
Go fast.

1711
02:06:12,850 --> 02:06:14,560
嘿 開快點
Hey, go fast.

1712
02:07:06,910 --> 02:07:08,910
Bhoomi 不要過來 快走
Bhoomi, don't come here. Go.

1713
02:09:29,880 --> 02:09:31,840
聽我的 快離開這里
Listen to me. Go from here.

1714
02:09:42,850 --> 02:09:44,060
哎呀 老爸
Oh god! Dad!

1715
02:09:47,730 --> 02:09:50,900
主人 是我錯了
Sir, It is wrong what l did.

1716
02:09:51,070 --> 02:09:52,450
我不該就那樣離開
I wouldn't have gone like that.

1717
02:09:53,110 --> 02:09:55,740
我本希望有你的保佑不會發生這種事的
I wished to happen everything by your blessing.

1718
02:09:56,160 --> 02:09:58,030
但是我實在沒辦法
But my situation is like that.

1719
02:09:58,290 --> 02:10:01,580
- 原諒我主人 - 我該原諒你嗎
-Pardon me sir. -Should I pardon you?

1720
02:10:07,750 --> 02:10:09,000
老爸
Dad!

1721
02:10:10,090 --> 02:10:12,670
不要啊 老爸 不要這樣對他
No dad! Don't do anything to him!

1722
02:10:12,760 --> 02:10:14,090
他沒做錯什么
He didn't do any mistake.

1723
02:10:14,720 --> 02:10:18,390
- 把她帶走 - Karthi 聽我說 老爸
-Take her away. -Karthi, listen to me. Dad!

1724
02:10:18,640 --> 02:10:19,430
放開我
Leave me!

1725
02:10:23,640 --> 02:10:25,020
主人 我不是有意的
Sir, I didn't do intentionally.

1726
02:10:26,060 --> 02:10:27,690
請理解我的處境
Please understand my situation.

1727
02:10:33,950 --> 02:10:36,320
我已經把Meera完璧歸趙了
I've handed over Meera safely to you.

1728
02:10:36,490 --> 02:10:37,370
還能怎樣
Then what?

1729
02:10:42,250 --> 02:10:44,370
放開我 天哪 Bhoomi
Leave me! Oh God! Bhoomi!

1730
02:10:47,840 --> 02:10:48,880
老爸 就一分鐘
Dad! One minute!

1731
02:10:49,210 --> 02:10:50,840
請聽聽他要說的話
Please understand what he is going to say.

1732
02:10:51,260 --> 02:10:52,590
他愛上了一個女孩
He loves a girl.

1733
02:10:52,670 --> 02:10:54,260
那女孩說會到火車站等他
She said that she have come to the station..

1734
02:10:54,340 --> 02:10:55,840
所以他才離開我去火車站的
..that's why he went there to leave me.

1735
02:10:56,090 --> 02:10:58,390
他沒做錯你想像的錯事
He didn't do any mistake as you think.

1736
02:11:00,010 --> 02:11:04,310
是的 主人 那個女孩子正在火車站等著我
Yes sir. She is waiting for me in the railway station.

1737
02:11:05,890 --> 02:11:08,810
如果我不去 她會
If I don't go then she will..

1738
02:11:09,570 --> 02:11:10,820
老爸 求你了
Dad! Please..

1739
02:11:11,320 --> 02:11:12,690
他說的都是真的
It is true what he is telling to you.

1740
02:11:13,110 --> 02:11:15,240
求求你放過他吧
Please leave him.

1741
02:11:17,110 --> 02:11:18,780
- 好 那你走吧 老爸
-Ok, you go. -Dad!

1742
02:11:21,700 --> 02:11:22,740
你可以走了
You can go!

1743
02:11:25,460 --> 02:11:26,620
再見 主人
Bye sir!

1744
02:11:29,170 --> 02:11:32,170
Meera我走了
Meera, I'll go.

1745
02:12:06,370 --> 02:12:11,460
那個時候你的父親想到的也許只有死亡
Your dad might think only about death at that time.

1746
02:12:11,960 --> 02:12:17,800
如果我沒有在最后一刻登上火車的話
If I didn't get into the train at the last minute that would happen.

1747
02:12:29,390 --> 02:12:30,900
火車就要到站了
Station will come soon.

1748
02:12:30,980 --> 02:12:32,810
把你的東西收拾好
Get ready with your things.

1749
02:12:33,020 --> 02:12:35,230
我還沒開完會 我在下節車廂
Meeting has not finished for me. I am in next cabin.

1750
02:12:40,280 --> 02:12:44,030
你有多愛我的媽媽
How much you loved my mother?

1751
02:12:50,040 --> 02:12:51,670
你怎么突然這么問
Why did you ask suddenly?

1752
02:12:52,170 --> 02:12:54,250
你媽媽就是我生命的全部
Your mother is life for me.

1753
02:12:56,460 --> 02:12:58,970
你媽媽也很愛我
Your mother also loved me very much.

1754
02:13:01,890 --> 02:13:03,510
她以前和我說 在她死之前
Before her death..

1755
02:13:03,850 --> 02:13:07,180
她不能回Semmanoor
She has told me that I wouldn't go to Semmanoor ever

1756
02:13:08,140 --> 02:13:11,640
我同意了 因為你很固執
I agreed because you were very stubborn.

1757
02:13:21,990 --> 02:13:24,490
歡迎 歡迎 路上還順利嗎
Come. How was your journey?

1758
02:13:24,910 --> 02:13:26,120
你兒子呢
Where is your son?

1759
02:13:26,200 --> 02:13:29,750
歡迎 歡迎 我在等你們呢
Come. l am waiting for you.

1760
02:13:43,470 --> 02:13:44,470
來吧
Come.

1761
02:13:48,970 --> 02:13:52,270
主人 看看是誰來了
Sir, see who has come!

1762
02:14:02,150 --> 02:14:04,610
Bhoomi 是你來了嗎 過來
Bhoomi, have you come? Come.

1763
02:14:04,740 --> 02:14:07,530
- 主人 你躺好 - 我沒事
-Sir, you take rest. -l am alright.

1764
02:14:08,160 --> 02:14:09,080
坐下吧
Sit down!

1765
02:14:12,120 --> 02:14:13,710
我以為你不會來的
I thought you wouldn't come.

1766
02:14:13,790 --> 02:14:16,170
我不會拒絕你的
Will I refuse your words?

1767
02:14:16,710 --> 02:14:18,880
Chakrapani說你要去澳大利亞
Chakrapani said that your next posting is in Australia..

1768
02:14:19,300 --> 02:14:22,090
中途經過這里
..and you have come to this town in the middle.

1769
02:14:22,220 --> 02:14:24,090
所以我想見見你
That's why I wanted to see you.

1770
02:14:24,890 --> 02:14:26,140
我妨礙你了嗎
Did I give you any trouble?

1771
02:14:27,140 --> 02:14:29,470
主人 哪有的事
Sir, what is this? Nothing like that.

1772
02:14:29,810 --> 02:14:30,970
有事盡管說 主人
You tell me sir.

1773
02:14:32,980 --> 02:14:36,600
我以為你會來問問Meera的事
I thought that you would ask about Meera when you come here.

1774
02:14:37,980 --> 02:14:39,610
可你一句都沒提
But you didn't ask anything.

1775
02:14:40,940 --> 02:14:43,940
對不起 我忘了 
Sorry! I forgot that.

1776
02:14:45,200 --> 02:14:47,660
Meera還好嗎 她在倫敦嗎
How is Meera? Is she in London?

1777
02:14:47,740 --> 02:14:49,740
還是已經回來了
Or has she come here?

1778
02:14:49,950 --> 02:14:52,200
Meera一直都在這里
Meera is here only.

1779
02:14:53,290 --> 02:14:54,500
在這里
Is she here?

1780
02:14:55,170 --> 02:14:57,710
那她為什么不出來呢
Then why didn't she come out?

1781
02:15:31,030 --> 02:15:32,240
你什么時候從倫敦回來的
When did you come from London?

1782
02:15:32,620 --> 02:15:34,290
你的丈夫孩子一起來了嗎
Have your husband and children come?

1783
02:15:34,450 --> 02:15:36,660
他們人呢 也在這里嗎
Where are they? Are they here?

1784
02:15:41,670 --> 02:15:43,590
Meera沒有結婚
Meera didn't marry anyone.

1785
02:15:45,130 --> 02:15:47,930
沒有結婚 為什么
Why didn't marry? Why?

1786
02:15:55,350 --> 02:15:57,390
我經常和我妻子說
I have told often to my wife.

1787
02:15:57,980 --> 02:16:02,570
誰娶到了Meera那真是好福氣
He'll be a lucky man who is going to marry Meera.

1788
02:16:04,990 --> 02:16:09,200
我沒找到那個有福的人
I couldn't find that lucky man.

1789
02:16:09,570 --> 02:16:10,950
她自己找到了
She found out.

1790
02:16:12,700 --> 02:16:16,000
但我不知道怎樣才能撮合他們
But I didn't know to unite them.

1791
02:16:19,960 --> 02:16:20,960
Meera 這是怎么回事
What is this Meera?

1792
02:16:21,630 --> 02:16:25,960
我沒想到今天見到你會是這個樣子
I didn't think that l'll be seeing you in this situation.

1793
02:16:26,630 --> 02:16:29,010
他們說你兒子和你一起來了
They said you brought your son with me.

1794
02:16:29,220 --> 02:16:31,840
他人呢 我還沒見過他
Where is he? I haven't seen him.

1795
02:16:47,360 --> 02:16:49,030
你知道她是誰嗎
Do you know who is she?

1796
02:16:50,280 --> 02:16:52,530
她就是Meera阿姨
She is Meera aunty.

1797
02:17:08,300 --> 02:17:09,470
可憐的Meera
Poor Meera!

1798
02:17:09,590 --> 02:17:12,930
她讓你爸爸去車站的時候
She didn't expect this situation..

1799
02:17:13,090 --> 02:17:15,850
她沒想到事情會這樣變化
..when she was lying them and sending your dad from there

1800
02:17:15,970 --> 02:17:18,640
老爸 求求你了 他說的都是真的
Dad please.. It is true what he is telling to you.

1801
02:17:18,850 --> 02:17:20,940
求求你放了他
Please leave him.

1802
02:17:21,140 --> 02:17:22,980
- 好 你走吧 - 老爸
-Ok, you go. -Dad!

1803
02:17:24,060 --> 02:17:24,900
你可走了 
You can go.

1804
02:17:26,070 --> 02:17:27,900
他在撒謊 別相信他
He said lie. Don't believe him.

1805
02:17:27,940 --> 02:17:29,610
我會查清楚是誰在撒謊的
I'll find out who is telling lie.

1806
02:17:29,740 --> 02:17:31,280
- Palani - 老板
-Palani -Sir!

1807
02:17:31,610 --> 02:17:32,740
你跟著他
You follow him.

1808
02:17:32,950 --> 02:17:35,120
如果真像他說的 有個女孩在火車上等他 你就放過他
You leave him when a girl is there as he told in the train.

1809
02:17:35,330 --> 02:17:37,410
- 否則就殺了他 - 是 老板
-Else you kill him. -Ok sir.

1810
02:17:45,130 --> 02:17:46,090
過來
Come.

1811
02:17:48,090 --> 02:17:49,300
他怎么知道的
How did he know?

1812
02:17:49,420 --> 02:17:52,090
所有人都在問我 可我什么都沒說
All are asking me. But I said no.

1813
02:17:52,180 --> 02:17:53,550
很好 跟我來 
That is good. Come with me.

1814
02:17:54,010 --> 02:17:55,550
你還要再幫我一個忙
You have to do one more help for me.

1815
02:17:55,890 --> 02:17:57,510
你去火車站和Bhoomi見面
You go to station and meet Bhoomi.

1816
02:17:57,760 --> 02:17:59,010
- 我 - 嗯 
-Me? -Yes!

1817
02:17:59,310 --> 02:18:00,930
我爸派了人去車站
Dad has sent the men to the station.

1818
02:18:01,020 --> 02:18:03,810
如果Bhoomi的愛人沒有出現的話 他們就會殺了他
He told to kill him if his lover is not there.

1819
02:18:03,900 --> 02:18:04,770
天哪
Oh God!

1820
02:18:04,900 --> 02:18:06,020
所以我才讓你去
That's why I am asking you to go.

1821
02:18:06,190 --> 02:18:08,110
Bhoomi現在必須知道真相了
Bhoomi has to know all truth now.

1822
02:18:08,400 --> 02:18:10,730
告訴他是我一直在打電話給他
Tell him that I have only spoken in the phone.

1823
02:18:11,820 --> 02:18:14,360
但是你要告訴他不要為了我回來打架
But you have to tell him that he shouldn't fight for me..

1824
02:18:14,610 --> 02:18:18,030
我會等他一輩子的
..and l would be waiting for him life long.

1825
02:18:21,450 --> 02:18:23,540
我這么說他會相信嗎
Will he believe me if I tell him all this?

1826
02:18:24,040 --> 02:18:25,370
我們沒其他辦法了
We have no way.

1827
02:18:25,580 --> 02:18:27,580
他沒有手機了
He doesn't have phone to call.

1828
02:18:28,920 --> 02:18:29,960
這樣吧
Else you do one thing.

1829
02:18:30,340 --> 02:18:31,300
你見到Bhoomi 然后打給我
You go there and call me.

1830
02:18:32,130 --> 02:18:33,590
我親口和她講清楚
I will tell everything to him.

1831
02:18:34,340 --> 02:18:36,390
快 快走 別讓任何人看見你
Go quickly without knowing to anyone.

1832
02:18:41,770 --> 02:18:44,230
這是末班車 后面沒有車了
There is no train after this. This is the last train.

1833
02:19:09,790 --> 02:19:22,060
快來
Come.

1834
02:20:02,510 --> 02:20:03,600
是你嗎
Is it you?

1835
02:20:06,140 --> 02:20:08,270
你早就可以告訴我了
You could have told me!

1836
02:20:11,020 --> 02:20:12,560
Bhoomi 我
Bhoomi, I am..

1837
02:20:33,420 --> 02:20:35,880
老板 他說的確實是實話
Yes sir! It is true what he said to me.

1838
02:20:36,010 --> 02:20:37,590
有個女孩和他在一起
A girl is with him.

1839
02:21:18,090 --> 02:21:22,930
我背叛了Meera 這不是一個朋友應該做的
I have betrayed Meera which a friend won't do ever.

1840
02:21:23,050 --> 02:21:23,970
可是不僅僅是我
Not only me.

1841
02:21:24,010 --> 02:21:29,180
誰會愿意放過這個嫁給他的機會呢
Who will miss such an opportunity to marry him?

1842
02:21:29,270 --> 02:21:35,190
所以我才把你父親帶到了很遠的地方
That's why I brought your dad so far away.

1843
02:21:35,440 --> 02:21:39,360
因為我的背叛 上天給了我懲罰
God has given the punishment because I did this betrayal.

1844
02:21:39,900 --> 02:21:46,200
他功成名就后 我卻沒這個好運和他長相廝守
I am not lucky to live with him who has achieved everything. Isn't it?

1845
02:21:47,370 --> 02:21:51,370
我死后很久你才會拿到這本日記
You will get this diary long after my death.

1846
02:21:51,410 --> 02:21:54,210
你要把這本日記銷毀掉 不要讓任何人看到
You should destroy it without anyone knowing it.

1847
02:21:55,540 --> 02:22:03,340
因為你的父親永遠不該知道真相
Because your dad shouldn't know this truth ever.

1848
02:22:13,560 --> 02:22:17,770
- 怎么了 怎么還不睡 - 我睡不著
-Why? Didn't you sleep? -l didn't get any sleep.

1849
02:22:19,110 --> 02:22:22,570
- Siddarth 你哭了嗎 － 沒有
-Siddarth, are you crying? -No.

1850
02:22:23,280 --> 02:22:25,950
別騙我 你爸爸不會騙人
Don't lie. Your dad wouldn't lie.

1851
02:22:26,030 --> 02:22:27,740
那他的兒子就不該騙人
Then his son also shouldn't lie.

1852
02:22:29,120 --> 02:22:29,990
你為什么哭了
Why did you cry?

1853
02:22:31,370 --> 02:22:33,210
我想我媽媽了
I remembered my mother.

1854
02:22:36,500 --> 02:22:40,300
睡吧 我會在這里陪著 直到你睡著
Sleep. I will be with you till you sleep.

1855
02:22:49,890 --> 02:22:53,430
阿姨 你會生我媽媽的氣嗎
Aunty, are you angry with my mom?

1856
02:22:54,940 --> 02:22:57,400
生氣 為什么
Angry? For what?

1857
02:22:59,270 --> 02:23:00,400
我不生她的氣
I am not angry with your mom.

1858
02:23:01,360 --> 02:23:02,820
我只是很難過
I felt very sad.

1859
02:23:03,700 --> 02:23:08,990
她去世之前一直都沒說要再見我
Your mom didn't say to meet me before her death.

1860
02:23:09,410 --> 02:23:11,620
所以我才覺得難過
That's why I felt very sad.

1861
02:23:12,330 --> 02:23:15,370
你該原諒我媽媽
You should forgive my mom.

1862
02:23:24,840 --> 02:23:31,010
我能活著見到你和你的兒子 當面請求你的原諒
I am alive to see you and your son and ask pardon to you.

1863
02:23:31,140 --> 02:23:32,930
