Sir, don't say like that.

1864
02:23:33,270 --> 02:23:37,440
我下次再來的時候 你會很健康的
You will be very healthy when I come next time.

1865
02:23:39,110 --> 02:23:41,150
那我告辭了
Then, l take leave.

1866
02:23:45,490 --> 02:23:47,820
和阿姨說再見
Say bye to her.

1867
02:23:56,870 --> 02:24:00,040
那你什么時候再來看我呢
When will you come to see me again?

1868
02:24:00,130 --> 02:24:04,130
我能叫你媽媽嗎
Shall I call you as mom?

1869
02:24:09,970 --> 02:24:12,300
可以 你可以叫我媽媽
Ok, you can call me.

1870
02:24:12,390 --> 02:24:16,480
那你能和我們一起走 做我的媽媽嗎
Then, will you come with me as my mom?

1871
