Say sorry to her.

1873
02:24:29,570 --> 02:24:30,990
我讓你快說道歉
I am telling you. Say sorry to her.

1874
02:24:31,070 --> 02:24:32,070
我不
I won't.

1875
02:24:43,420 --> 02:24:44,420
